Echoedreaming - Untouched [single]

The single before the second album.
7 minutes of pure dreamy improvisation on alternate tuned electric guitars with custom gauge string-set.

In this musical experience, I explored forms of expression through unusual playstyle and arrangement. I have made the sound landscape of something untouched, unknown place.

The magical sounds on a background is the result of shimmering reverb/echoes, not keys.  

Instruments: 
electric bass, drum machine, electric guitars, pedals.
